OL,4,CSchools told not to teach about gender
OL,5,Cidentity
OL,6,GSchools in England should not teach
OL,7,Gabout gender identity, according to
OL,8,Gnew draft guidance from the government.
OL,10,FGovernment sources told BBC News about
OL,11,Fplans to ban sex education for under-
OL,12,Fnines, as well as teaching about
OL,13,Fgender identity, on Wednesday.
OL,15,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak said the
OL,16,Fnew guidance would ensure children
OL,17,Fwere not "exposed to disturbing
OL,18,Fcontent".
OL,20,FSome teachers have said there is no
OL,21,Fevidence of a widespread problem.
